  "title": "[사당동 성장 클리닉/사당동한의원/이수한의원]성장/키 크는 한약/키 크는 방법",
  "addDate": "2013. 3. 18.",
  "categoryNo": "10",
  "parentCategoryNo": "9",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=110163416678",
  "html_size": 190521,
  "body": "<div id=\"post-view110163416678\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea110163416678\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'3028108_10';\" class=\"view\"><div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'3028108_10';\" class=\"view\"> \r\n<div class=\"view\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '3028108_10'\">\r\n<div class=\"view\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '3028108_10'\">\r\n<div class=\"view\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 10pt; FONT-FAMILY: '3028108_10'\">\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">[성장/키 크는 한약/키 크는 방법]</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">키 크는 방법에 관심을 두는 부모님들이 많으십니다</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">특히 성장클리닉 상담을 하게 되면 첫 질문이</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;'우리 아이는 키가 안커요 왜 안클까요?'</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">이수한의원에서 우리아이들의 성장, 키 크기 방법에 대해서 알아보겠습니다&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/db30cc773470496a.png\" width=\"469\" height=\"354\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 469px; rheight: 354px\" id=\"20130318_296/isuhani_1363580521720CnOsv_PNG/%BC%BA%C0%E5%B1%D7%B8%B22.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6405666')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/db30cc773470496a.png\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"COLOR: #3a32c3\">우리 아이 키가 안커요</span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">아이들의 키가 큰다는 것은 단순한 키의 증가 뿐만아니라 체충,뇌, 심장 등 장기의</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">무게와 기능이 조화롭게 커가는 과정을 말합니다</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">아이들의 키가 크는 시기에는 키의 성장 뿐만 아니라 인체의 면역력을 튼튼히 하고</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">내부 장기의 균형이 잘 이루어지도록 도와줘야 합니다</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130318_58/isuhani_1363576583433dmAvM_JPEG/%B2%D9%B9%CC%B1%E2%BC%BA%C0%E5%C7%A51%BC%BA%C0%E5%C7%A51.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"510\" height=\"373\" style=\"cursor: pointer;BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rwidth: 510px; rheight: 373px\" id=\"20130318_58/isuhani_1363576583433dmAvM_JPEG/%B2%D9%B9%CC%B1%E2%BC%BA%C0%E5%C7%A51%BC%BA%C0%E5%C7%A51.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6405666')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130318_58/isuhani_1363576583433dmAvM_JPEG/%B2%D9%B9%CC%B1%E2%BC%BA%C0%E5%C7%A51%BC%BA%C0%E5%C7%A51.jpg?type=w3\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - 유전적 : 아버지 키가 166cm이하, 어머니 키가 156cm이하인 경우 유전적 저신장증</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;- 영양부족 : 편식이 심하거나 먹는양이 적은 경우 성장에 필요한 영양분 부족으로 </p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 키가 안크게 되고, 반대로 소아 비만인 경우에도 키 성장에 방해가 됩니다</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -&nbsp; 운동 : 운동량이 적으면 성장판이 자극되지 않아 성장 호르몬 분비가 원활하지 않게</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;되어 키가 잘 안 크게 됩니다</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130318_131/isuhani_1363576584561wtPu1_JPEG/%B2%D9%B9%CC%B1%E2%BC%BA%C0%E5%C7%A51%BC%BA%C0%E5%C7%A52.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"515\" height=\"364\" style=\"cursor: pointer;BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rwidth: 515px; rheight: 364px\" id=\"20130318_131/isuhani_1363576584561wtPu1_JPEG/%B2%D9%B9%CC%B1%E2%BC%BA%C0%E5%C7%A51%BC%BA%C0%E5%C7%A52.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6405666')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20130318_131/isuhani_1363576584561wtPu1_JPEG/%B2%D9%B9%CC%B1%E2%BC%BA%C0%E5%C7%A51%BC%BA%C0%E5%C7%A52.jpg?type=w3\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - 질병 : 호르몬 결핍으로 인한 갑상선 이상, 염색체 이상으로 인한 터너증후군, </p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 소아형 당뇨가 있는 경우 키가 잘 안크게 됩니다</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; - 수면 : 성장 호르몬이 분비되는 밤 10시~새벽2시 사이에 </p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;잠을 자지 않으면 키가 잘 안 크는 원인이 될수 있습니다</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;- 스트레스 :&nbsp;아이들도 성인처럼 정신적 스트레스를 받고 있습니다</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 성장 호르몬에 영향을 주어 키가 안&nbsp;크는 원인이 될 수 있습니다&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\" align=\"left\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><br style=\"CLEAR: both\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/0d903e7f6f3ae123.png\" width=\"545\" height=\"318\" style=\"cursor: pointer;BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rwidth: 545px; rheight: 318px\" id=\"20130318_206/isuhani_1363576608254uGurp_PNG/%BC%BA%C0%E5%C7%A53.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6405666')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/0d903e7f6f3ae123.png\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">키 크는 한약은 언제 먹는게 좋을까?</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">여아 - 만&nbsp; 9세이전 </p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">남아 - 만 11세이전</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">이 나이 때가 성장 치료의 효과를 극대화 시킵니다</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><u><span style=\"COLOR: #ef007c\"><u><strong>사당 이수 한의원</strong></u></span> 에서는 성장침, 성장탕(면역력 강화및성장판의 기능 촉진)체형교정</u></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><u>으로 키 크는 데 도움을 주고 , 소화기가 약하거나 스트레스등을 해소시켜</u></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><u>키 성장에 방해를 막아 줍니다</u></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div align=\"center\"><div>\n<iframe src=\"https://mashup.map.naver.com/view.nhn?mid=bl012921843%40s13104608&type=total\" width=\"402\" height=\"352\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" onerror=\"return true;\" onabort=\"return true;\" style=\"margin:18px 0;padding:8px;background-color:white;\" title=\"포스트에 첨부된 지도\"></iframe>\n</div></div>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\"><a class=\"con_link\" href=\"http://blog.naver.com/isuhani\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/725a69ab743633a1.png\" width=\"266\" height=\"66\" style=\"cursor: pointer;BORDER-LEFT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-BOTTOM-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-TOP-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); BORDER-RIGHT-COLOR: rgb(0,0,0); rwidth: 266px; rheight: 66px\" id=\"20130318_9/isuhani_1363585884356NGdwp_PNG/2013-03-18_14%3B49%3B33.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6405666')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/725a69ab743633a1.png\"></a></p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\" align=\"center\">&nbsp;</p></div></div></div></div></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
